title: Diana, Scandalous photo's leaked!
body:
[](http://i.imgur.com/ytxyQ5K.jpg?noredirect)

Revealing photo's of one of the League's most heretical champions have been leaked to the public by an unknown source (We have speculations that a certain Radiant champion may to be to blame, however we cannot confirm this) !

http://www.mobafire.com/images/avatars/janna-forecast.png : WOAH! Carl, i thought we wernt gunna use that one... It's a little much for daytime TV. Gunna have to edit that one out. This next one according to my notes is her without any make up on... hm
